 first ancestor grabbing mushu and pulling away from the post you had yourchance to protect the fa family 
 ancestor your led fa deng to disaster 
 fa deng with his decapitated head on his lap yeah thanks a lot 
 mushu and your point is 
 first ancestor the point is we will be sending a real dragon to retrievemulan 
 mushu what but a real dragon 
 first ancestor grabbing mushu and pulling him away from the guardian post asmushu fights to hold on you are not worthy of this spot now awaken thegreat stone dragon first ancestor throws mushu out of the temple 
 mushu looking back into the temple so get back to me on the jobthing 
 an ancestor throws gong and hits mushu in the face 
 mushu walking with a slouch and banging the gong on the ground just onechance is that too much to ask i mean not like kill ya 
 mushu rings the gong and looks at the great stone dragon yo rocky wakeup you gotta go fetch mulan pauses as nothing happens mushu walks overto the side of the statue boy go get her go on throws the gongstick off the screen and whistles come on angrily while climbing up thegreat stone dragon grrr grrrr speaking in his ear and banging the earwith the gong hello helloooooo curtly hello bangs the gong extra hardagainst the ear causing it to break off uh oh the great stone dragoncrumbles to the ground head intact minus the ear knocks on the uh stoney stooooneeey oh man gonna kill me 
 first ancestor calling out through the temple window great stone you awaken 
 mushu holding the head of the great stone dragon up to that first ancestorcan only see head and body uhhh yes i just woke up and iam the great stone dragon good morning mushu waves i will go forth andfetch mulan did did i mention that i was the great stone dragon 
 first ancestor go the fate of the fa family rests in your claws 
 mushu even worry about it i will not lose face mushu falls downthe hill under the weight of the great stone head and lands on pedestal with the head falling on top of him 
 mushu muffled ow my elbow aw aw i know i twisted something throwing the head off him just great now what doomed andall cause miss man decides to take her little drag show on the road 
 enters stage right 
 chirp chirp 
 mushu go get her the matter with you after this great stonehumpty dumpty mess have to bring her home with a medal to get back in thetemple wait a minute it i make mulan a war hero then bebegging me to come back to work the master plan oh gone anddone it now mushu runs off stage right 
 hopping along side of mushu chirp chirp chirp chirp 
 mushu pushing away hey what makes you think coming 
 chirp chirp 
 mushu lucky ho ho heh do i look like a sucker to you 
 chirp chirp 
 mushu whach you mean loser how bout i pop one of your off andthrow it across the yard then a loser me or you 
 interlude 
 cut to leading his army at a charge on horseback through a forest he stops and motions stage right hun archer hun strong guy hun dismount and walk into the forest they throw down two imperial scoutsbefore the rest of the army 
 hun guy imperial scouts 
 shan yu dismounts and walks towards the scouts 
 scout 
 he crouches down in front of them 
 adjusting scout s collar nice work gentlemen you found thehun army motioning to the soldiers on horseback the hun army laughs 
 scout the emperor will stop you 
 grabs scout by the shirt collar and lifts him up to his face stop me he invited me by building his wall he challenged my strength well here to play his game throws scout to the ground andpoints his sword at scout as he gets up and runs calling out to thescouts go tell your emperor to send his strongest armies quietly 
 the imperial scouts run off towards the palace 
 scratching his chin how many men does it take to deliver amessage 
 archer guy drawing back his bow one 
 end interlude 
